GENERAL
We are committed to keep your data secure, your private information private, and being transparent about our practices. We adhere to the best practices to secure information collected from You.
At INDmoney, we take privacy and security seriously. This Privacy Policy outlines how INDmoney , its parent entity Finzoom Investment Advisors Private limited and its subsidiaries including but not limited to Finzoomers Services Private Limited, INDmoney Private Limited, ADfi Digital Private Limited, INDmoney Global (IFSC) Private Limited (collectively, “INDmoney,” “we,” “our,” or “us” or “Company”) process the information that we collect about you through our websites, mobile apps, and other online services and when you otherwise interact with us, such as through our customer care service channels. The Company owns, operates and manages a website having domain name
https://www.indmoney.com/
,
https://www.indstocks.com/
and related software application for use on wireless computing devices such as smartphones and tablets and also for use on desktop or laptop computers under the name and style of “INDmoney”, "INDstocks / INDstocks by INDmoney" (collectively hereinafter referred to as
“Platform”
or
“Application”).
The Platform enables Users to seamlessly access a diverse array of online financial products and services including, in relation to stock broking services, mutual fund execution, insurance distribution, US Stocks investment, National Pension System (NPS) services, opening online digital savings accounts, facilitating with the digital loan disbursement, digital payment services through the United Payments Interface (UPI), and facilitating bill payment services to the Users ("Services"). These Services are subject to the Platform's applicable Terms and Conditions, as detailed at
https://www.indmoney.com/terms-of-services
and for INDstocks at
https://www.indstocks.com/page/terms-conditions-indian-stocks
. We are committed to safeguarding the personal information shared by Users and ensure it is handled in line with robust privacy standards and legal frameworks.
